	The <resolution> tag is used for the setCoordinateResolution() function.
	
	You may move, add or delete any controls you want as long as they're not Required.
	With one exception, required controls <description> tag and <type> tag MUST NOT be changed.
	The exception is <type>label</type> may be changed to <type>button</type>.	This allows 
	<shadowcolor> tag to be used. (set <texturenofocus>-</texturenofocus> if doing this.)
		
